{"tid":895882,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！貓仔走失","createTime":"2018-11-09T14:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T02:30:27.000Z","uid":126087,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"73bf6c95e9ad5281a176c2932518d096cf486291","tid":895882,"uid":126087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:17:44.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n我隻貓仔11歲<br />\n性格內向細膽<br />\n尋晚走失咗 (住井字型公屋)<br />\n逐層周圍巡都搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n平時開門佢會出去走廊行下趴下<br />\n識自己返歸<br />\n有人經過會即刻沖返屋企<br />\n但係尋晚搵唔到佢<br />\n驚佢係自己走咗去其他層俾痴線佬追佢捉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常如果入咗人地屋企 <br />\n屋主應該會同管理處講<br />\n但係到依家都無消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好擔心佢<br />\n我都知衰<br />\n唔應該咁樣放佢出去咁玩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢快啲返屋企"},{"pid":"59b4a01e8d2befcbf35432f481f84163f5c0e331","tid":895882,"uid":126087,"like":0,"dislike":40,"score":-40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"依家考慮緊搵動物傳心師睇下會唔會有佢消息<br />\n呢個動物傳心協會睇落好似有信心啲<br />\n但係唔知係咪有用<br />\nfb有個成功案例<br />\n但唔知係咪真<br />\n想問下有無巴絲試過動物傳心有用？<br />\n我都明<br />\n呢啲信則有不信則無嘅<br />\n但係幾百蚊可以令貓仔返歸<br />\n俾多幾倍都肯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/09/221828_e7b4f81110003c9f3a4bb674243fbc76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F221828_e7b4f81110003c9f3a4bb674243fbc76.png&h=bb22d97f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/09/221836_becc3d73495e27c58d714cc6c026589c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F221836_becc3d73495e27c58d714cc6c026589c.png&h=5f77ca17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/09/221853_b687a42237c80c8195d5c22422d62ff3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F09%2F221853_b687a42237c80c8195d5c22422d62ff3.png&h=486a6990&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ea6f5322d49fe363c303029902d6bdb621a5bff","tid":895882,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T14:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3492e7401ccf8948114b8ed4b0c5de2e396ef927","tid":895882,"uid":126087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n開頭諗住係夜晚啲人趕住訓覺懶得理<br />\n或者有啲人想等個主人出告示再俾返隻貓人地<br />\n收下錢咁<br />\n但係告示貼咗一日都未有回音<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519518d5261d9d88c0c3cb1468b737799fe3501d","tid":895882,"uid":36849,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb177a7cf227cef39a67606b20cfd071072159b4","tid":895882,"uid":76063,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T15:55:51.000Z","msg":"你有冇腦架"},{"pid":"6c49c60127c7417152e70a5df1e796316a2f6c57","tid":895882,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T16:01:14.000Z","msg":"你住幾樓？ 會唔會跳左落樓？<br />\n由自己個層逐間屋禁鐘問啦"},{"pid":"9ca38322b4e677cb15f40a7cff126eb20b9354f2","tid":895882,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:11:15.000Z","msg":"相又無，地點又無，post 張傳心師相出黎把撚咩"},{"pid":"4198e92a18419ad1c8d38043c12b301ca39ad419","tid":895882,"uid":21052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:20:39.000Z","msg":"我幫你搵<br />\n1000蚊<br />\n識動